57
00:03:11.198 --> 00:03:15.348
The Beneish M-Score is
based on eight ratios.

58
00:03:15.348 --> 00:03:19.420
A higher M-Score means higher
likelihood of manipulation.

59
00:03:19.420 --> 00:03:22.100
