incentives to manipulate earnings.

82
00:04:44.940 --> 00:04:46.070
The Depreciation Index,

83
00:04:46.070 --> 00:04:51.890
or DEPI, is gonna be prior depreciation
rate over current depreciation rate,

84
00:04:51.890 --> 00:04:56.850
where depreciation rate is depreciation
divided by depreciation plus PP&E.

85
00:04:56.850 --> 00:05:00.690
A ratio greater than one could indicate
the depreciation rate has slowed,

